WEBVTT

00:00:02.696 --> 00:00:03.796
What do you two think you're doing?

00:00:05.596 --> 00:00:07.166
(Episode 33)

00:00:07.226 --> 00:00:10.296
I knew you were up to something when you played innocent for your dad.

00:00:12.736 --> 00:00:14.906
Your father will be thrilled when he finds out, won't he?

00:00:16.276 --> 00:00:17.436
He's fired. Effective immediately.

00:00:18.906 --> 00:00:20.206
You can't do that, Mom.

00:00:20.706 --> 00:00:22.416
The fact that Woo Jin is trying to get a liver transplant.

00:00:22.916 --> 00:00:24.346
Should I go ahead and tell Dad about that?

00:00:27.916 --> 00:00:28.916
You...

00:00:29.656 --> 00:00:31.556
So that's how you found out. You were tracking me.

00:00:34.626 --> 00:00:37.026
How dare you put a tracking device on my car?

00:00:38.866 --> 00:00:40.196
You did the same thing to me.

00:00:40.526 --> 00:00:42.336
I did that to keep you from getting out of line,

00:00:42.736 --> 00:00:47.066
and to make you a desirable bride. It was for your own protection.

00:00:47.236 --> 00:00:48.976
I did it for myself, too.

00:00:49.876 --> 00:00:51.746
By tailing me just so you could blackmail me?

00:00:54.916 --> 00:00:55.946
Even if I tried to explain,

00:00:56.446 --> 00:00:59.186
- you wouldn't understand. - You...

00:01:01.346 --> 00:01:03.756
Yes. Something did seem off about you.

00:01:04.486 --> 00:01:06.926
I couldn't put my finger on it, but you'd changed.

00:01:08.496 --> 00:01:09.826
So it was all because of him, wasn't it?

00:01:10.526 --> 00:01:13.426
- Did he put you up to this? - It's not like that.

00:01:13.496 --> 00:01:16.096
Not like that? Then why were you two so cosy?

00:01:16.596 --> 00:01:19.436
Do you realise how hard I've worked to keep your reputation pristine?

00:01:19.506 --> 00:01:21.876
That's what made you such a prime catch.

00:01:23.676 --> 00:01:25.606
What we should be talking about right now...

00:01:26.606 --> 00:01:28.006
is Woo Jin.

00:01:34.846 --> 00:01:37.516
You'd really tell Dad about Woo Jin's transplant situation?

00:01:38.586 --> 00:01:40.726
Even though you know exactly what that would do to our family?

00:01:41.756 --> 00:01:44.026
You won't do it.

00:01:45.626 --> 00:01:46.666
Yes, I will.

00:01:48.666 --> 00:01:50.266
If Dad finds out and loses it,

00:01:50.736 --> 00:01:52.136
you're the one who's going to get hurt,

00:01:53.006 --> 00:01:54.206
not me.

00:01:55.676 --> 00:01:56.676
And what about you?

00:01:57.076 --> 00:01:58.745
What will he do when he learns the bodyguard he hired...

00:01:58.746 --> 00:02:00.206
fooled around with you?

00:02:01.206 --> 00:02:04.276
There's nothing he hates more than betrayal by someone he trusts.

00:02:04.446 --> 00:02:06.146
What do you think will happen to you and that punk?

00:02:06.246 --> 00:02:08.486
It's not like that between Ji Wan and me.

00:02:08.756 --> 00:02:11.416
- We're not even dating. - Don't lie to me. I saw you myself.

00:02:11.486 --> 00:02:12.486
Mom.

00:02:14.426 --> 00:02:17.126
If I say it's not true, shouldn't you just believe me?

00:02:19.526 --> 00:02:21.666
I can be completely honest with Dad.

00:02:23.536 --> 00:02:25.636
It's true that Ji Wan and I got close,

00:02:26.266 --> 00:02:30.306
but I have a clear conscience. I can look Dad right in the eye...

00:02:30.806 --> 00:02:32.676
and tell him the complete truth.

00:02:35.846 --> 00:02:36.876
What did you just say?

00:02:38.786 --> 00:02:39.816
But...

00:02:41.586 --> 00:02:44.416
there's no reason for either of us to upset Dad right now, is there?

00:02:49.696 --> 00:02:50.756
But, Mom...

00:02:52.526 --> 00:02:54.866
Why did you hide that Woo Jin was sick?

00:03:04.576 --> 00:03:05.806
All right. Fine.

00:03:07.506 --> 00:03:08.516
Go ahead. Have your fun.

00:03:10.446 --> 00:03:11.546
Come to think of it,

00:03:12.046 --> 00:03:14.146
maybe it's because you've never had the chance to let loose.

00:03:14.716 --> 00:03:15.716
But...

00:03:16.286 --> 00:03:17.756
as for you and him fooling around,

00:03:18.626 --> 00:03:21.386
I can't stop your father from finding out on his own.

00:03:26.926 --> 00:03:28.636
And you keep your mouth shut about Woo Jin.

00:03:32.436 --> 00:03:33.536
Understood.

00:03:37.776 --> 00:03:39.506
Should I really be waiting out here?

00:03:39.846 --> 00:03:43.016
Director Ko wouldn't hit her, would she?

00:03:45.616 --> 00:03:46.616
Oh, no.

00:04:06.406 --> 00:04:07.436
Yeong Ra.

00:04:09.906 --> 00:04:10.936
How did it go?

00:04:11.076 --> 00:04:13.906
She said she'd tell my dad and get you fired,

00:04:14.446 --> 00:04:18.146
so I threatened to tell him she hid Woo Jin's liver transplant.

00:04:19.886 --> 00:04:20.886
You did what?

00:04:22.186 --> 00:04:24.156
I had no other choice.

00:04:25.326 --> 00:04:26.486
No, I mean...

00:04:27.256 --> 00:04:29.196
What possessed you to do that?

00:04:31.456 --> 00:04:34.366
She saw us in such a weird situation.

00:04:34.766 --> 00:04:36.566
And it's not like my mom is someone you can reason with.

00:04:36.996 --> 00:04:40.406
But I couldn't just stand by and let you get fired.

00:04:41.936 --> 00:04:43.836
Before I knew it, the words...

00:04:44.406 --> 00:04:45.576
just came blurting out.

00:04:46.806 --> 00:04:49.046
Wait, so you're saying...

00:04:49.616 --> 00:04:52.916
you just cut a deal with Director Ko?

00:04:55.356 --> 00:04:57.386
So? Did it work?

00:04:57.816 --> 00:05:00.886
- And she agreed to your terms? - She didn't have a choice.

00:05:01.456 --> 00:05:02.826
She lied to my dad.

00:05:03.856 --> 00:05:06.366
This is a huge deal.

00:05:06.496 --> 00:05:09.796
So, does this mean I can keep my job?

00:05:10.036 --> 00:05:12.836
Of course. That's the whole reason I made a deal with her.

00:05:15.636 --> 00:05:17.136
By the way, Ji Wan.

00:05:17.706 --> 00:05:19.246
We're signing with Neiro tomorrow, right?

00:05:19.576 --> 00:05:20.576
Why?

00:05:21.206 --> 00:05:22.776
- Nervous? - No.

00:05:23.276 --> 00:05:24.346
I'm just eager to get started.

00:05:28.046 --> 00:05:30.056
That little brat thinks she can threaten me?

00:05:32.626 --> 00:05:35.726
That punk she's with must have given her the idea.

00:05:37.596 --> 00:05:38.796
Fine.

00:05:39.326 --> 00:05:40.626
Go ahead. Do your worst.

00:05:41.896 --> 00:05:44.796
Because I'm going to put everything right back where it belongs.

00:05:46.506 --> 00:05:49.076
- I'm home. - Hey.

00:05:52.106 --> 00:05:54.476
- Dad, you're home early. - Yes, I am.

00:05:55.416 --> 00:05:57.876
Yeong Ra, sit down. We need to talk.

00:06:04.156 --> 00:06:07.956
Honey. Apparently, Yeong Ra's decided to stop painting.

00:06:08.026 --> 00:06:09.096
She says it's too much for her.

00:06:10.356 --> 00:06:14.196
She realised it after her solo show. She just wants to do it as a hobby.

00:06:16.936 --> 00:06:19.766
You must have had a tough time preparing for your solo show.

00:06:21.106 --> 00:06:23.636
It's true, being an artist is no easy feat.

00:06:24.006 --> 00:06:26.506
Yeong Ra is starting to get tech neck.

00:06:27.546 --> 00:06:28.646
Right, Yeong Ra?

00:06:28.916 --> 00:06:32.046
You don't want to be stuck at an easel all day, do you?

00:06:33.916 --> 00:06:34.916
Right.

00:06:36.186 --> 00:06:37.556
What is Mom up to?

00:06:39.086 --> 00:06:43.626
Yeong Ra turns 26 in the new year. She needs to get married next year,

00:06:43.756 --> 00:06:45.156
while she's in her prime.

00:06:46.366 --> 00:06:50.936
I think Yeong Ra should run her own gallery.

00:06:51.766 --> 00:06:53.766
You could even set one up for her, couldn't you?

00:06:53.966 --> 00:06:55.936
I suppose so.

00:06:56.706 --> 00:06:59.246
It's not like women just support men from home these days.

00:07:01.106 --> 00:07:04.016
So I'm going to clear out Yeong Ra's art studio.

00:07:05.446 --> 00:07:07.486
- What? - Why so suddenly?

00:07:09.086 --> 00:07:11.186
Since no one's home during the day anyway,

00:07:11.656 --> 00:07:14.325
she can relax and do her hobbies...

00:07:14.326 --> 00:07:16.526
while working on her graduate thesis.

00:07:16.726 --> 00:07:21.566
There's time for classes, cooking, Pilates, and English lessons.

00:07:23.166 --> 00:07:25.066
Yeong Ra, if that's what you want, go for it.

00:07:26.136 --> 00:07:29.236
She's trying to take our space away from Ji Wan and me.

00:07:30.236 --> 00:07:35.146
Honey, can we let Ji Wan stay on as her bodyguard?

00:07:35.816 --> 00:07:39.516
The trial date is set, but the verdict is months away.

00:07:40.316 --> 00:07:41.916
Of course.

00:07:43.686 --> 00:07:45.626
I didn't fire Lee Ji Wan.

00:07:46.126 --> 00:07:47.126
Happy now?

00:07:49.926 --> 00:07:52.866
I wasn't going to be an artist forever anyway.

00:07:53.226 --> 00:07:55.366
I always thought the studio was too big.

00:07:57.096 --> 00:07:58.736
I'll clear my stuff out first thing.

00:08:09.346 --> 00:08:12.146
Emergency! We're in huge trouble.

00:08:12.216 --> 00:08:13.416
(Emergency! We're in huge trouble.)

00:08:19.086 --> 00:08:21.326
(Damga Charcoal Grill)

00:08:24.096 --> 00:08:26.866
Just tell her this liver transplant is about saving a life.

00:08:27.566 --> 00:08:29.436
That's all you need to say to your sister.

00:08:30.736 --> 00:08:32.236
I'm done in the kitchen.

00:08:32.936 --> 00:08:33.936
I'm done too.

00:08:35.476 --> 00:08:38.176
Mom, when is Eun Oh getting admitted to the hospital?

00:08:38.236 --> 00:08:39.546
Why would your sister be admitted?

00:08:39.976 --> 00:08:42.546
Oh, that. She decided not to go through with it.

00:08:43.676 --> 00:08:47.046
She told you she's backing out? So she must be really scared.

00:08:47.616 --> 00:08:50.556
It's not like my sister to back out after she already set the date.

00:08:51.186 --> 00:08:53.686
What reason did she give? That she's scared?

00:08:55.126 --> 00:08:57.126
- Hey. - You two look wiped out.

00:08:57.526 --> 00:08:58.726
Hey, what brings you here?

00:08:59.996 --> 00:09:01.326
I need to talk to you.

00:09:02.036 --> 00:09:03.036
Funny you should say that.

00:09:03.336 --> 00:09:06.436
Because today, I'm the one who needs to talk to Mom.

00:09:07.036 --> 00:09:09.336
Here? All right, we can all talk together then.

00:09:09.876 --> 00:09:12.106
No, not today.

00:09:12.676 --> 00:09:15.376
Gang Oh, grab two bottles of soju for us, and you can head out.

00:09:16.016 --> 00:09:17.076
Soju?

00:09:17.776 --> 00:09:18.846
Eun Oh, what is it?

00:09:23.916 --> 00:09:25.426
So that woman...

00:09:26.226 --> 00:09:30.726
I found proof she only sought me out for the liver transplant.

00:09:31.126 --> 00:09:32.226
So that's what happened.

00:09:32.896 --> 00:09:33.896
My goodness...

00:09:35.666 --> 00:09:37.236
So that's what was going on all along.

00:09:38.366 --> 00:09:39.536
No wonder...

00:09:40.836 --> 00:09:41.966
I know.

00:09:44.436 --> 00:09:46.746
You must've been suffering so much, my poor girl.

00:09:49.276 --> 00:09:50.576
I'm still suffering.

00:09:51.746 --> 00:09:54.086
What can I do to help? What? What do you need?

00:09:54.186 --> 00:09:57.616
Should I go find that woman and make sure she never returns?

00:09:57.686 --> 00:09:59.526
Should I just break both her legs?

00:10:01.926 --> 00:10:03.156
Don't do anything.

00:10:03.656 --> 00:10:06.226
She won't come looking for me again.

00:10:07.396 --> 00:10:10.866
She won't be able to change my mind. I made that clear to her.

00:10:12.236 --> 00:10:13.236
I even...

00:10:14.736 --> 00:10:16.376
I even told her I wouldn't do it...

00:10:17.236 --> 00:10:19.006
specifically because he's her son.

00:10:21.546 --> 00:10:23.116
My goodness.

00:10:24.576 --> 00:10:26.486
That must have torn you up inside.

00:10:27.446 --> 00:10:29.356
She tore your heart to shreds.

00:10:34.956 --> 00:10:35.956
Mom.

00:10:36.756 --> 00:10:40.626
Thanks for holding back your tears and listening to me.

00:10:42.026 --> 00:10:45.936
But I can see you're trying so hard not to cry.

00:10:46.966 --> 00:10:50.876
Crying over a woman like that would be a waste of tears.

00:10:59.046 --> 00:11:00.046
Ji Gang Oh.

00:11:00.716 --> 00:11:01.716
Oh, hey.

00:11:02.786 --> 00:11:05.986
What? Were you waiting out here in case Mom and I got into a fight?

00:11:06.686 --> 00:11:08.026
No, it's not that.

00:11:09.156 --> 00:11:10.225
So what did you two talk about?

00:11:10.226 --> 00:11:11.626
- What? - Oh, boy.

00:11:11.756 --> 00:11:14.466
Mom, why don't you tell Gang Oh everything?

00:11:14.926 --> 00:11:17.796
He's my brother, so he should know too.

00:11:18.436 --> 00:11:20.136
So, she was only after the liver from the start?

00:11:20.706 --> 00:11:23.606
That's what she said. That evil witch.

00:11:23.736 --> 00:11:26.445
How can she be so shameless?

00:11:26.446 --> 00:11:28.406
I know she abandoned Eun Oh, but she's still her daughter.

00:11:29.176 --> 00:11:30.646
Gosh, what a piece of work.

00:11:31.176 --> 00:11:35.046
But thank goodness Eun Oh found out before the transplant.

00:11:35.116 --> 00:11:36.985
Exactly. She can't have the surgery...

00:11:36.986 --> 00:11:38.926
- for a crazy person like that. - Exactly.

00:11:43.926 --> 00:11:44.926
What's wrong?

00:11:49.336 --> 00:11:50.336
Mom.

00:11:51.066 --> 00:11:52.906
I'm in big trouble.

00:11:53.736 --> 00:11:55.206
I really messed up.

00:11:56.676 --> 00:11:57.876
What did you do?

00:11:59.146 --> 00:12:00.776
I just assumed she would go through with the surgery,

00:12:01.206 --> 00:12:03.946
so when her birth mom offered money, I took it.

00:12:04.276 --> 00:12:05.276
What?

00:12:06.416 --> 00:12:08.816
She said she was going to give us thank-you money anyway.

00:12:08.886 --> 00:12:10.856
When I thought about it from her perspective,

00:12:10.916 --> 00:12:13.486
- it only seemed right she pay us. - So wait.

00:12:14.126 --> 00:12:16.126
You took the money? Is that what you're saying?

00:12:16.756 --> 00:12:17.856
How much?

00:12:20.766 --> 00:12:22.396
Five hundred thousand dollars.

00:12:23.266 --> 00:12:26.206
You... Are you crazy?

00:12:26.266 --> 00:12:30.636
Are you insane? You took money from the woman who wanted her liver?

00:12:30.706 --> 00:12:32.976
- I can't believe this. You fool! - Gosh, that hurts.

00:12:33.876 --> 00:12:36.846
You're going to be the death of me! I swear, you really are!

00:12:39.846 --> 00:12:41.146
I haven't spent a single penny.

00:12:42.046 --> 00:12:43.056
For real.

00:12:46.826 --> 00:12:48.386
That venomous, evil woman.

00:12:49.556 --> 00:12:51.956
Doing whatever it takes to steal Eun Oh's liver.

00:12:52.466 --> 00:12:53.466
Unbelievable.

00:12:54.466 --> 00:12:56.166
I'll return it tomorrow and set her straight.

00:12:56.236 --> 00:12:57.366
And I'll apologise to Eun Oh.

00:12:57.696 --> 00:13:00.436
- No, I will beg for forgiveness. - But, my sister...

00:13:03.176 --> 00:13:04.206
Let's keep this a secret from her.

00:13:04.606 --> 00:13:05.606
What?

00:13:06.946 --> 00:13:07.946
You...

00:13:09.176 --> 00:13:11.346
Don't you ever tell Eun Oh you took that money.

00:13:12.616 --> 00:13:15.085
She's already heartbroken over...

00:13:15.086 --> 00:13:17.186
what her birth mother is truly like.

00:13:17.316 --> 00:13:20.986
What if she finds out her own brother was paid off?

00:13:21.626 --> 00:13:23.456
How devastated do you think she'd be?

00:13:26.396 --> 00:13:28.426
It would crush Eun Oh. We can't do that to her.

00:13:31.396 --> 00:13:33.806
You lunatic. You fool!

00:13:40.376 --> 00:13:42.076
I guess you'd better start looking for a place.

00:13:42.716 --> 00:13:44.316
Where at? Somewhere around here?

00:13:45.016 --> 00:13:47.345
I'm torn between a studio near work...

00:13:47.346 --> 00:13:49.716
or a one-bedroom apartment in Eun Oh's neighbourhood.

00:13:50.116 --> 00:13:51.616
I haven't decided yet.

00:13:52.156 --> 00:13:53.656
Why? Is it because of Eun Oh?

00:13:54.856 --> 00:13:55.856
Yes, pretty much.

00:13:59.896 --> 00:14:01.266
Dreaming of a future together?

00:14:02.466 --> 00:14:05.536
It's not like I'm planning it out. I just can't help but picture it.

00:14:06.536 --> 00:14:09.506
I can't imagine my life without Eun Oh in it anymore.

00:14:11.836 --> 00:14:13.206
Man, Ji Hyuk. Who knew?

00:14:14.546 --> 00:14:16.916
I guess this is what they mean when they say timing is everything.

00:14:19.516 --> 00:14:20.516
Wait.

00:14:20.986 --> 00:14:21.986
It's about time for Eun Oh to get here.

00:14:22.486 --> 00:14:24.656
- Hey, in front of Eun Oh... - Relax, I won't say a thing.

00:14:24.916 --> 00:14:26.856
Would I say I'm relieved she now knows who her birth mother is,

00:14:26.926 --> 00:14:29.056
or that I'm glad she's not doing the liver transplant?

00:14:30.196 --> 00:14:33.866
There's nothing anyone can say to comfort Eun Oh right now.

00:14:40.806 --> 00:14:41.806
Sir.

00:14:42.406 --> 00:14:44.206
- My gosh. - There's more.

00:14:44.276 --> 00:14:45.336
Here, let me get those.

00:14:46.876 --> 00:14:48.546
Thanks. You can get back to your work.

00:15:08.166 --> 00:15:10.866
Director Ko really knows how to hit you where it hurts.

00:15:11.466 --> 00:15:14.536
So her goal is to get rid of any place we can be together.

00:15:16.206 --> 00:15:19.676
So, does that mean we shouldn't sign the contract today?

00:15:20.576 --> 00:15:23.346
She could have people come and clear this place out as early as tomorrow.

00:15:24.876 --> 00:15:27.016
Gosh, where are you going to draw your webtoon then?

00:15:29.986 --> 00:15:32.526
Should we find you a new studio?

00:15:33.886 --> 00:15:34.926
A studio?

00:15:35.186 --> 00:15:37.456
You're getting a 3,000-dollar signing bonus.

00:15:37.696 --> 00:15:41.826
A studio for 3,000 dollars? Come on, that's way too small.

00:15:41.966 --> 00:15:45.436
Look, new artists like you don't normally get a signing bonus.

00:15:45.736 --> 00:15:47.336
Usually, you just get paid an artist's fee per episode.

00:15:47.406 --> 00:15:50.336
They only gave you a signing bonus because you were so reluctant.

00:15:50.836 --> 00:15:51.976
What did you just say?

00:15:52.946 --> 00:15:53.946
An "artist's fee?"

00:15:54.576 --> 00:15:58.146
Yes, for artists, it's called a creator's fee.

00:16:01.386 --> 00:16:03.716
A "creator's fee." That sounds so cool.

00:16:04.286 --> 00:16:05.826
Let's find our studio right away, Ji Wan.

00:16:06.156 --> 00:16:09.196
I can just pay for it myself, right? How much do we need?

00:16:09.496 --> 00:16:11.096
A 50,000-dollar deposit? 100,000?

00:16:11.496 --> 00:16:13.566
- One hundred thousand? - Let's just find one fast.

00:16:14.226 --> 00:16:17.036
It'll be fine as long as I'm the one to break it to my dad.

00:16:17.466 --> 00:16:21.406
I've already figured out what to say so Mom can't argue.

00:16:23.136 --> 00:16:27.076
Like mother, like daughter. You have a trick up your sleeve too?

00:16:28.776 --> 00:16:30.876
Because I want to keep drawing my webtoon.

00:16:33.386 --> 00:16:34.386
In that case, Yeong Ra...

00:16:35.586 --> 00:16:39.956
If you're using your own money, why not use what you've earned?

00:16:40.426 --> 00:16:43.756
As it's a studio for your webtoon, you could use your signing bonus.

00:16:44.356 --> 00:16:45.526
With the 3,000 dollars?

00:16:47.126 --> 00:16:50.636
You can pay the rent with the fee you get for each episode.

00:16:52.536 --> 00:16:55.536
